# Global vs Per-Layout Configuration

::: info
**Global Configuration**
- Defined in FrontMatter
- Applies to all slides
- Easy maintenance
- Guaranteed consistency
:::

::: success
**Per-Layout** ⭐ **Powerful**
- Specific to each slide type
- Maximum flexibility
- Contextual headers/footers
- Better user experience
:::

::: warning
**Per Individual Slide**
- Specific override
- Maximum granular control
- For special cases
- Requires more configuration
:::

